This directory (ex_model_Ar_P_MLJ_F03) contains a modified Lennard Jones (LJ)
Model with smoothed cutoff radius written in F03.  It complies with
the KIM API library, supporting all NBCs and Locator and Iterator mode, and
publishes its parameters, and supports optional computation of `energy',
`forces', `particleEnergy', and `virial'.


The following files are in this directory (before any compilation is performed):

LICENSE.CDDL
     The Common Development and Distribution License (CDDL) Version 1.0 file

Makefile
     Makefile to build executables with GNU or Intel compilers

README
     this file

ex_model_Ar_P_MLJ_F03.F03
     F03 file that contains the implementation of the modified LJ
     potential.

model_Ar_P_MLJ_F03.kim
     KIM descriptor file, contains all variables and methods that are exposed
     through the KIM API interface.
